race.description: Troppo Jacks Tuncurry Beach Bowling Club Maiden Handicap
race.comment: NAMARA (3) did a good job last start to finish third at Tamworth over 1200m, beaten one length. Cherry-ripe now and expected to get off the mark. HELIOPHILE (5) missed the placings two runs back then was never in contention last start when ninth over 1106m at Port Macquarie. Can turn things around with the winkers being applied. AELFWYNN (8) is a four-start maiden who finished seventh at her most recent appearance over 1300m at Newcastle. Likely to be in the finish in this suitable assignment. WHISKERS (4) deep into the prep and showed plenty of fight with a handy third over 1106m at Port Macquarie. Maps well and can play a leading role.
